generateEmptyMethodBody

public void generateEmptyMethodBody(String methodName,
                                    String returnType)
Generates an empty method body.

If you type: 

 
    writer.generateEmptyMethodBody("MyEntity", "stableId");

The following method body will be generated: 

 
     MyEntity stableId();
